1270
00:58:56,000 --> 00:58:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve mi se čini su ljudi razumijeli.

1271
00:58:58,000 --> 00:59:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uglavnom su prespavali.

1272
00:59:00,000 --> 00:59:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sve mi nešto govori.

1273
00:59:02,000 --> 00:59:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate lupa po meni.

1274
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta si ću govoriti.

1275
00:59:04,000 --> 00:59:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to toga ništa.

1276
00:59:05,000 --> 00:59:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to i nije ništa si govorio.

1277
00:59:06,000 --> 00:59:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ima neko zlo.

1278
00:59:08,000 --> 00:59:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koje hoće da je razvoreno dobro što sam učinio.

1279
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zanimljivo tada sam počin govoriti.

1280
00:59:14,000 --> 00:59:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da je ovo bilo odlično.

1281
00:59:16,000 --> 00:59:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da su ljudi čuli.

1282
00:59:18,000 --> 00:59:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da će oni reći da je to izvrsno.

1283
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem.

1284
00:59:21,000 --> 00:59:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno deset puta ja se mi kažem.

1285
00:59:23,000 --> 00:59:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda u meni ostaje kao jedna nutarnja snaga.

1286
00:59:27,000 --> 00:59:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao nešto se u mene uvriježilo.

1287
00:59:29,000 --> 00:59:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan temelj koji stano govori da.

1288
00:59:31,000 --> 00:59:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je odlično.

1289
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to će biti dobro.

1290
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to vjerujem.

1291
00:59:34,000 --> 00:59:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uvijek doživio da ljudi dolaze u pauze.

1292
00:59:37,000 --> 00:59:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Profesore odakle.

1293
00:59:38,000 --> 00:59:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Profesore kako sam vos poznao.

1294
00:59:42,000 --> 00:59:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tad sam shvatio zašto Isus kaže.

1295
00:59:46,000 --> 00:59:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onome koji vjeruje svoje moguće.

1296
00:59:48,000 --> 00:59:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zašto kaže.

1297
00:59:50,000 --> 00:59:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerajte to je spasno.

1298
00:59:52,000 --> 00:59:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte teže bolesti možete ozrebiti.

1299
00:59:54,000 --> 00:59:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mojga žena.

1300
00:59:56,000 --> 00:59:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada je oprosila temelj.

1301
00:59:58,000 --> 00:59:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle vjerovala o to.

1302
00:59:59,000 --> 01:00:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ostavno li treba na operaciju.

1303
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Raka na prsima.

1304
01:00:03,000 --> 01:00:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bezbroj tih situacija.

1305
01:00:05,000 --> 01:00:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi je tako jasno.

1306
01:00:07,000 --> 01:00:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad počeš vjerovati.

1307
01:00:09,000 --> 01:00:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada nešto povučeš cijeli semir za sobom.

1308
01:00:11,000 --> 01:00:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve se mijenja.

1309
01:00:13,000 --> 01:00:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro to je vjera.

1310
01:00:15,000 --> 01:00:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad tako govoriš.

1311
01:00:16,000 --> 01:00:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ove četiri točke o kojima sam govorio.

1312
01:00:18,000 --> 01:00:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] One ne samo da mijenjaju druge.

1313
01:00:20,000 --> 01:00:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi smo uglavnom to analizirali.

1314
01:00:22,000 --> 01:00:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je bitno kod tih četiri točke.

1315
01:00:24,000 --> 01:00:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je one tebe mijenjaju.

1316
01:00:26,000 --> 01:00:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] One tebe čine sretim.

1317
01:00:27,000 --> 01:00:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] One tebe ozdravljuju.

1318
01:00:29,000 --> 01:00:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prva točka kad kažeš ja ti opraštam.

1319
01:00:33,000 --> 01:00:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] I druga točka kad kažeš oprostiti meni.

1320
01:00:38,000 --> 01:00:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Već te dvije točke sto put sam osjetio.

1321
01:00:41,000 --> 01:00:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neko me uvrijedio.

1322
01:00:42,000 --> 01:00:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] S nekim ne mogu.

1323
01:00:43,000 --> 01:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono i tamo je bezobrazan.

1324
01:00:44,000 --> 01:00:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono i tamo ovakav.

1325
01:00:45,000 --> 01:00:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje ne mogu.

1326
01:00:46,000 --> 01:00:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Umoran sam.

1327
01:00:47,000 --> 01:00:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad već te dvije točke napravim.

1328
01:00:50,000 --> 01:00:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja oživim.

1329
01:00:52,000 --> 01:00:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam zdrav.

1330
01:00:55,000 --> 01:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uspješan.

1331
01:00:56,000 --> 01:00:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] A nevjerojatno.

1332
01:00:58,000 --> 01:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] A još ako nastavim sa one druge dvije.

1333
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema granica.

1334
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle što se događa kad ja kažem opraštam ti.

1335
01:01:06,000 --> 01:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada ja zapravo.

1336
01:01:09,000 --> 01:01:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao sam vam to sto puta.

1337
01:01:11,000 --> 01:01:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad mene neko uvrijedi.

1338
01:01:13,000 --> 01:01:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad te neko uvrijedi.

1339
01:01:14,000 --> 01:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da ubaci u tebe neku bombu koja je aktivirana.

1340
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ako ti to čuvaš u sebi.

1341
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti o tome razmišljaš.

1342
01:01:22,000 --> 01:01:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zašto mi je to.

1343
01:01:23,000 --> 01:01:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa za kako mogu to reći.

1344
01:01:24,000 --> 01:01:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ovo pa ono.

1345
01:01:25,000 --> 01:01:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti u sebi samo čuvaš tu bombu koja će svaki čas predirati.

1346
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razori će.

1347
01:01:29,000 --> 01:01:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tvoje misli.

1348
01:01:30,000 --> 01:01:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tvoji intelekt.

1349
01:01:31,000 --> 01:01:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tvoji moral.

1350
01:01:32,000 --> 01:01:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ono što je u tebi vrijedno i dragoceno.

1351
01:01:34,000 --> 01:01:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] To razara.

1352
01:01:35,000 --> 01:01:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa gore nego razmišljati onome koji te uvrijedio.

1353
01:01:39,000 --> 01:01:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razori će.

1354
01:01:40,000 --> 01:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda još nešto te boli.

1355
01:01:41,000 --> 01:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa osjećaš da ne možeš ni misliti.

1356
01:01:43,000 --> 01:01:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Emocije su ranjene.

1357
01:01:44,000 --> 01:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Um je ranjen.

1358
01:01:45,000 --> 01:01:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razum ranjen.

1359
01:01:46,000 --> 01:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećaš da ne možeš ni raditi.

1360
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možeš ni jesti.

1361
01:01:48,000 --> 01:01:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da se ni spava.

1362
01:01:49,000 --> 01:01:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] To krećeš se sto put ovo.

1363
01:01:51,000 --> 01:01:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ubija braćo moja.

1364
01:01:53,000 --> 01:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka uvreda.

1365
01:01:55,000 --> 01:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna negativna riječ koja ti kaže.

1366
01:01:57,000 --> 01:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ti to stoji samo tvoja koza.

1367
01:01:59,000 --> 01:02:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to izgledaš.

1368
01:02:01,000 --> 01:02:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ćeš takav ići.

1369
01:02:03,000 --> 01:02:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Može srano da je bilo.

1370
01:02:04,000 --> 01:02:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ta boja kravate ne ide.

1371
01:02:06,000 --> 01:02:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pusti ga čovječe.

1372
01:02:08,000 --> 01:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje i tako dalje.

1373
01:02:13,000 --> 01:02:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čim nekome rekneš nešto negativno.

1374
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si ga ranio teško.

1375
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ta rana boli.

1376
01:02:18,000 --> 01:02:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si ubacio u njega bombu.

1377
01:02:20,000 --> 01:02:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on se muči.

1378
01:02:21,000 --> 01:02:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] To boli duboko prijatelji.

1379
01:02:23,000 --> 01:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vlastiti grijeh nikad toliko ne boli.

1380
01:02:26,000 --> 01:02:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko boli.

1381
01:02:27,000 --> 01:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tuđi grijeh.

1382
01:02:28,000 --> 01:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji ti je povrijedio.

1383
01:02:29,000 --> 01:02:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji ti je nešto negativno rekao.

1384
01:02:31,000 --> 01:02:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osobno kad povredi.

1385
01:02:32,000 --> 01:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je dostojanstvo.

1386
01:02:33,000 --> 01:02:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je osobnost.

1387
01:02:34,000 --> 01:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] To boli užasno.

1388
01:02:36,000 --> 01:02:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] A onda kad ti još pošli predvacivati.

1389
01:02:38,000 --> 01:02:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ti si kriv.

1390
01:02:39,000 --> 01:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] A tko drugi?

1391
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da pa nič ne radiš.

1392
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sram te bilo.

1393
01:02:42,000 --> 01:02:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si ko mali pakao.

1394
01:02:44,000 --> 01:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ću mi kaži.

1395
01:02:46,000 --> 01:02:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro idem se ubić da ću.

1396
01:02:47,000 --> 01:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ne znate koliko riječi ubijaju.

1397
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih rekao.

1398
01:02:54,000 --> 01:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije toliko opaso kad te muž udari.

1399
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Fizički.

1400
01:02:57,000 --> 01:03:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad njega žena jezikom lupi.

1401
01:03:00,000 --> 01:03:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neizlječivo.

1402
01:03:04,000 --> 01:03:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I niko ne govori o tom nasilju prijatelji dragi.

1403
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ženima je tako oštar jezik da je milina.

1404
01:03:17,000 --> 01:03:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] A dečki je oštru ruku.

1405
01:03:22,000 --> 01:03:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kako izići dakle iz tog pakla nasilja.

1406
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Istog zapravo zarobljeništva.

1407
01:03:27,000 --> 01:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] A to boli užasno.

1408
01:03:29,000 --> 01:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Još predvacivanje.

1409
01:03:33,000 --> 01:03:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nikad neće to da popraviš.

1410
01:03:35,000 --> 01:03:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta radiš mužu?

1411
01:03:36,000 --> 01:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] A žena šta ti radiš.

1412
01:03:37,000 --> 01:03:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gledaj.

1413
01:03:38,000 --> 01:03:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kak si to ispekla?

1414
01:03:39,000 --> 01:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zar ti ovo nemaš pametnije kruha kupiti?

1415
01:03:41,000 --> 01:03:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kak ti stoji ta haljena?

1416
01:03:43,000 --> 01:03:43,000
[UNKNOWN] Ajde molite.

1417
01:03:43,000 --> 01:03:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Holjena ti se vide.

1418
01:03:44,000 --> 01:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sram te bilo.

1419
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

1420
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad počnu tako predvacivati gotovo i prijatelji.

1421
01:03:49,000 --> 01:03:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je kada ubaciješ u njega bombe.

1422
01:03:52,000 --> 01:03:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ako se hoćeš sloboditi, nema druge nego bomu izbaciti van.

1423
01:03:59,000 --> 01:04:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako dalje.

1424
01:04:00,000 --> 01:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi stari znamo to.

1425
01:04:02,000 --> 01:04:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rad naš domovinski.

1426
01:04:04,000 --> 01:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od bomba se može sakriti.

1427
01:04:06,000 --> 01:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to da su me mrzili.

1428
01:04:07,000 --> 01:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] To da su me progonuli.

1429
01:04:08,000 --> 01:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] To da su me psovali.

1430
01:04:09,000 --> 01:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] To da su me ružili.

1431
01:04:10,000 --> 01:04:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] To da su me htjeli uzeti moju domovinu.

1432
01:04:12,000 --> 01:04:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moju slobodu.

1433
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moju majku.

1434
01:04:14,000 --> 01:04:15,000
[UNKNOWN] Moga oca.

1435
01:04:15,000 --> 01:04:17,000
[UNKNOWN] To je užasno.

1436
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to muči.

1437
01:04:18,000 --> 01:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] I naši branitelji se zato ubijaju.

1438
01:04:21,000 --> 01:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je post traumatski.

1439
01:04:23,000 --> 01:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sredstni sindrom.

1440
01:04:25,000 --> 01:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi svi smo zapravo mrtvi.

1441
01:04:28,000 --> 01:04:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mrzimo, mrzimo.

1442
01:04:30,000 --> 01:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo još mudri pa kažemo:

1443
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro razdaj se može oprostiti pa gleda šta su napravili.

1444
01:04:34,000 --> 01:04:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao daj šta šta sad?

1445
01:04:36,000 --> 01:04:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čuvaj tu bombu u sebe da tebe razvori.

1446
01:04:38,000 --> 01:04:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti me ćeš to svetiti neprijatelju.

1447
01:04:40,000 --> 01:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gluposti.

1448
01:04:43,000 --> 01:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako si u nekoj kući uvijek taj primjer uzimam.

1449
01:04:45,000 --> 01:04:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] U ratu sam to vidio.

1450
01:04:46,000 --> 01:04:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neprijatelj dođe da vuče se pa ubaci aktiviranu bombu tebe u kuću.

1451
01:04:50,000 --> 01:04:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ču uzeti pa gledati:

1452
01:04:51,000 --> 01:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, dobra bombica.

1453
01:04:52,000 --> 01:04:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] I on joj razmišljati ili ćeš brže van pa njemu.

1454
01:04:57,000 --> 01:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono.

1455
01:04:59,000 --> 01:05:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oprostiti prijatelja znači ubiti neprijatelja.

1456
01:05:02,000 --> 01:05:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ubiti neprijatelja, a izliječiti vlastitu opasnost, ranu i strahu.

1457
01:05:07,000 --> 01:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad praštaš, ti ne pomažeš ništa neprijatelju.

1458
01:05:12,000 --> 01:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad mu oprosiš, neće on doći u nebo.

1459
01:05:14,000 --> 01:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne boj se.

1460
01:05:15,000 --> 01:05:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam prava na ništa kad ti mu oprosiš.

1461
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino što je u tom oproštenju, to je:

1462
01:05:20,000 --> 01:05:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si slobodan od njegova zla.

1463
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on ti ne možeš ništa.

1464
01:05:23,000 --> 01:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti mu se sviješ.

1465
01:05:24,000 --> 01:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod nas o slavonju, to znaju ljudi reći kad neka povrijediva,

1466
01:05:31,000 --> 01:05:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je uvijek druga, ili žena druga, ono znaju reći:

1467
01:05:34,000 --> 01:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A pjuni mi pod prozor.

1468
01:05:36,000 --> 01:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] To znači to ne ulazi u mene.

1469
01:05:39,000 --> 01:05:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je izvan mene i prema tome ne možeš vam vrijediti.

1470
01:05:41,000 --> 01:05:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je mudra rečenica zapravo,

1471
01:05:43,000 --> 01:05:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] poslije kad sam o tome razmišljao.

1472
01:05:46,000 --> 01:05:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa opasi nego ne prestano se mučiti,

1473
01:05:51,000 --> 01:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] sa odmijen što ti je neko ubacio.

1474
01:05:53,000 --> 01:05:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je gore od svih bombi.

1475
01:05:56,000 --> 01:05:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I praštanje nije ništa drugo nego oslobođenje.

1476
01:05:59,000 --> 01:06:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nećeš ti mene.

1477
01:06:00,000 --> 01:06:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to kako ćeš to osloboditi?

1478
01:06:02,000 --> 01:06:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da misliš:

1479
01:06:03,000 --> 01:06:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] A jadan on?

1480
01:06:04,000 --> 01:06:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako možeš tako negativno govoriti?

1481
01:06:06,000 --> 01:06:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to muž?

1482
01:06:08,000 --> 01:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoja majka?

1483
01:06:09,000 --> 01:06:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoja žena?

1484
01:06:10,000 --> 01:06:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoje djete?

1485
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoj otac?

1486
01:06:12,000 --> 01:06:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoj susjed?

1487
01:06:13,000 --> 01:06:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to tvoj prijatelj?

1488
01:06:14,000 --> 01:06:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to kolegica na koju?

1489
01:06:15,000 --> 01:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bih:

1490
01:06:16,000 --> 01:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako možeš?

1491
01:06:17,000 --> 01:06:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da razmisli.

1492
01:06:18,000 --> 01:06:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako možeš tako negativno reći?

1493
01:06:20,000 --> 01:06:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako može tu lažic raziti?

1494
01:06:22,000 --> 01:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam najbolja žena na svijetu.

1495
01:06:24,000 --> 01:06:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja?

1496
01:06:26,000 --> 01:06:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nema tako muškarca.

1497
01:06:27,000 --> 01:06:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo ja.

1498
01:06:28,000 --> 01:06:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek moraš pozitivno o sebi govoriti

1499
01:06:31,000 --> 01:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] i požaliti onoga.

1500
01:06:32,000 --> 01:06:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako može biti takav zlo?

1501
01:06:34,000 --> 01:06:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ćeš se uspjeti osloboditi.

1502
01:06:37,000 --> 01:06:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dok leko dosadneš ono drugo.

1503
01:06:40,000 --> 01:06:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to mogao?

1504
01:06:41,000 --> 01:06:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sramo je bilo.

1505
01:06:42,000 --> 01:06:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa on je još gorio od mene.

1506
01:06:43,000 --> 01:06:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti samo vidiš kako umnažaš zlo.

1507
01:06:44,000 --> 01:06:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mržnju, osvetu, negativne riječi,

1508
01:06:47,000 --> 01:06:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] negativne mislije.

1509
01:06:48,000 --> 01:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti sebe, sebe truješ, uništavaš i gaziš.

1510
01:06:51,000 --> 01:06:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ta mudrost.

1511
01:06:54,000 --> 01:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad ti oprosiš,

1512
01:06:55,000 --> 01:06:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda vidiš:

1513
01:06:56,000 --> 01:06:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Joj Bože moj,

1514
01:06:57,000 --> 01:06:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] smiješ se ovako ko ja stanu.

1515
01:06:59,000 --> 01:07:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Smijat se mogu te kad ja dođem ovdje na mikrofon

1516
01:07:05,000 --> 01:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda gledam se vas i kažem:

1517
01:07:07,000 --> 01:07:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] U sebi ja vam od srca praštam ljudi.

1518
01:07:09,000 --> 01:07:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vam praštam.

1519
01:07:10,000 --> 01:07:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vam se rezumijem.

1520
01:07:11,000 --> 01:07:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možete biti kakvi hoćete.

1521
01:07:13,000 --> 01:07:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja vas neću suditi.

1522
01:07:16,000 --> 01:07:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa prosite i vi meni,

1523
01:07:18,000 --> 01:07:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] što nisam još bolji.

1524
01:07:20,000 --> 01:07:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] A htio bi biti, vjerujte mi.

1525
01:07:22,000 --> 01:07:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kažem:

1526
01:07:24,000 --> 01:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hoću vas voljeti.

1527
01:07:25,000 --> 01:07:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Htio bi vas roditi kao dobar otac svoju djecu.

1528
01:07:28,000 --> 01:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju:

1529
01:07:29,000 --> 01:07:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, ja ti zahvaljuju što sam mi daro ove ljude.

1530
01:07:32,000 --> 01:07:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta bi bilo da njih nema?

1531
01:07:34,000 --> 01:07:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ba da vas sve moje znanje i moj život.

1532
01:07:37,000 --> 01:07:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, gled koliko rađam.

1533
01:07:39,000 --> 01:07:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kad utisnem u vas ono dobro, vi ste novi ljudi.

1534
01:07:43,000 --> 01:07:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nova je domovina.

1535
01:07:44,000 --> 01:07:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Novi svijet.

1536
01:07:47,000 --> 01:07:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad to oproštenje zapravo mijenja mene.

1537
01:07:50,000 --> 01:07:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sto put sam vidio, prijatelje drage,

1538
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada idem u kuće ili u kuću.

1539
01:07:56,000 --> 01:08:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem u neke posle ili susrstenke ljudima za koje znam povrijedili su me.

1540
01:08:00,000 --> 01:08:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, ne mogu ni misliti na njega.

1541
01:08:02,000 --> 01:08:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda samo znam jedno, dok idem ili već prije toga.

1542
01:08:05,000 --> 01:08:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo gledam u duhu.

1543
01:08:06,000 --> 01:08:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ti opraštam.

1544
01:08:08,000 --> 01:08:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Potpuno ti opraštam.

1545
01:08:09,000 --> 01:08:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Može biti kako hoćeš.

1546
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam osjećam kao da nešto s mene silazi.

1547
01:08:12,000 --> 01:08:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja idem uz srta čovjeka.

1548
01:08:14,000 --> 01:08:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu se smijati mirno.

1549
01:08:16,000 --> 01:08:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ja kažem oprašati, znači ja neću ni jednu riječ spomenuti negativnu.

1550
01:08:21,000 --> 01:08:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja te neću suditi.

1551
01:08:22,000 --> 01:08:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja te neću nikada suditi.

1552
01:08:24,000 --> 01:08:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ja ne.

1553
01:08:25,000 --> 01:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer Jezus kaže ne sudite i ne osuđujte.

1554
01:08:27,000 --> 01:08:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako tebi osuđam, ja sam osuđam.

1555
01:08:29,000 --> 01:08:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi sam ljud.

1556
01:08:30,000 --> 01:08:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je ta mudrost koju treba znati.

1557
01:08:32,000 --> 01:08:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to su te rane duhovne koje su sasvim drugačije od fizičkih rana.

1558
01:08:36,000 --> 01:08:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ako njih ne slatiš u tom paradoksalnom zapravo svome jednom porođaju u tebi,

1559
01:08:42,000 --> 01:08:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] nećeš se zato osloboditi.

1560
01:08:44,000 --> 01:08:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tako napraviti.

1561
01:08:45,000 --> 01:08:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] I posveš sposoban susreci svakog čovjeka.

1562
01:08:48,000 --> 01:08:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne znam kako si imao protiv njega.

1563
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] može se protiv njega.

1564
01:08:52,000 --> 01:08:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Može se ogovara, olagao protiv njega.

1565
01:08:53,000 --> 01:08:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad te stid može prići k njemu.

1566
01:08:55,000 --> 01:08:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] A čiji kaže samo to u sebi, opraštam ti.

1567
01:08:58,000 --> 01:09:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda polako dodaš, oprosti ti meni.

1568
01:09:01,000 --> 01:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da oprosti, negativno sam mislio protiv tebe.

1569
01:09:03,000 --> 01:09:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Družao sam te.

1570
01:09:05,000 --> 01:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo u sebi osjehao.

1571
01:09:07,000 --> 01:09:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Žao mi je.

1572
01:09:08,000 --> 01:09:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oprosti mi.

1573
01:09:09,000 --> 01:09:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je čudo kako postaješ slobodan.

1574
01:09:11,000 --> 01:09:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Točno osjećam kako mi proradi i želudac i pluča i srce i glava i mozak.

1575
01:09:16,000 --> 01:09:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve zdravo.

1576
01:09:18,000 --> 01:09:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako to ostane u tebi sve, onda ne možeš spavati.

1577
01:09:21,000 --> 01:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Krvotok se stisne i krv neće kako treba.

1578
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pluča su stisnute i ne mogu primati zraha.

1579
01:09:27,000 --> 01:09:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možeš duboko udaviti.

1580
01:09:29,000 --> 01:09:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si gotov.

1581
01:09:30,000 --> 01:09:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Žile u nogama se stišću, vene su gotove i ti ne boš hodati.

1582
01:09:34,000 --> 01:09:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Želju da stisne pravi rak.

1583
01:09:36,000 --> 01:09:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mora rak, ali dobro čir.

1584
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] A crema opet hemoroida i tako.

1585
01:09:40,000 --> 01:09:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svatimo dakle da jedna takva uvreda napravi tisuću bolesti.

1586
01:09:45,000 --> 01:09:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I mi se napitamo kako to.

1587
01:09:47,000 --> 01:09:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] I liječeci mi kažu, profesor dajte mi protumačite.

1588
01:09:49,000 --> 01:09:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osobito ono kardiologa zamis prita, ali znam isto liječnike, serebra i druge kolege, prijatelje.

1589
01:09:54,000 --> 01:09:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma to mi se ove zamis i dođe mi kaže.

1590
01:09:57,000 --> 01:10:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže ima te i te probleme sa želucem, sa srcem, osobitom.

1591
01:10:00,000 --> 01:10:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa glavom i sa tako dalje.

1592
01:10:02,000 --> 01:10:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zdražim, nema ništa, ništa, ništa.

1593
01:10:04,000 --> 01:10:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, ne znaš šta.

1594
01:10:06,000 --> 01:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda znam da smo učili, kaže, psihofizički treba.

1595
01:10:09,000 --> 01:10:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Promatrati psihosomatski.

1596
01:10:12,000 --> 01:10:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda pokušavam, kaže, psihički to nema, ne znam što.

1597
01:10:16,000 --> 01:10:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto? Na psihičkoj razi nikad nećeš za toga.

1598
01:10:18,000 --> 01:10:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi neko pogledio? Jesi činio zlo protiv njega?

1599
01:10:22,000 --> 01:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi oprostio? To nema.

1600
01:10:24,000 --> 01:10:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ostaje bolesti.

1601
01:10:26,000 --> 01:10:27,000
[UNKNOWN] Jesi šta ću?

1602
01:10:27,000 --> 01:10:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dam nekoliko lijekova samo da simptomatski se malo pomogne.

1603
01:10:30,000 --> 01:10:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to ne liječi.

1604
01:10:32,000 --> 01:10:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otkloni simptome da te ne boli.

1605
01:10:34,000 --> 01:10:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Glava za dva, tri sata i za toga još gore.

1606
01:10:36,000 --> 01:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako izliječiti, pitaju.

1607
01:10:38,000 --> 01:10:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma vi ne znate koliko sam ih robo ja ti sretim da nam Bog dao to otkriće duhovne dimenzije.

1608
01:10:43,000 --> 01:10:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je u tome.

1609
01:10:45,000 --> 01:10:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čitavo društvo ćemo promijeniti.

1610
01:10:48,000 --> 01:10:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve bolesti moći liječiti, prijatelji dragi.

1611
01:10:50,000 --> 01:10:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi će ti ljudi moći biti prijatelji.

1612
01:10:52,000 --> 01:10:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti znaš put kako da liješiš.

1613
01:10:54,000 --> 01:10:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da se olakšaš.

1614
01:10:55,000 --> 01:10:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da u tebi funkcionira svaki organ.

1615
01:10:57,000 --> 01:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da duša se veseli.

1616
01:10:59,000 --> 01:11:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da budeš kreativor.

1617
01:11:00,000 --> 01:11:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da stvaraš, pižeš.

1618
01:11:02,000 --> 01:11:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako da se ne baviš ni jednom negativnom mišlju.

1619
01:11:04,000 --> 01:11:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ni jednom bolešću.

1620
01:11:05,000 --> 01:11:05,000
[UNKNOWN] Ničim.

1621
01:11:05,000 --> 01:11:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne.

1622
01:11:06,000 --> 01:11:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakve zraha.

1623
01:11:07,000 --> 01:11:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] To s tim ti nemaš ništa.

1624
01:11:09,000 --> 01:11:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kad ne vjeriš u strah.

1625
01:11:10,000 --> 01:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ne vjeriš u bolest.

1626
01:11:11,000 --> 01:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vjeriš u prijatnje.

1627
01:11:12,000 --> 01:11:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada si slobodan i tada.

1628
01:11:14,000 --> 01:11:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada sigurno, sigurno uspjevaš.

1629
01:11:16,000 --> 01:11:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to dobro u kojem ti vjeruješ.

1630
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tjera i zle ljude.

1631
01:11:19,000 --> 01:11:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zlo iz njih.

1632
01:11:20,000 --> 01:11:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mijenja njih.

1633
01:11:21,000 --> 01:11:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali osobito mijenja i slobađa tebe.

1634
01:11:23,000 --> 01:11:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj tjedan.

1635
01:11:26,000 --> 01:11:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ove dvije stvari za sad napravite.

1636
01:11:28,000 --> 01:11:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da naučite svako jutro čim ustaješ.

1637
01:11:31,000 --> 01:11:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onda se sjeti.

1638
01:11:32,000 --> 01:11:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koga će sve danas sresti.

1639
01:11:34,000 --> 01:11:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I odmah gledaš ga u oči.

1640
01:11:37,000 --> 01:11:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] U duhu i samog.

1641
01:11:39,000 --> 01:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Opraštaj ti.

1642
01:11:40,000 --> 01:11:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neću te suditi.

1643
01:11:42,000 --> 01:11:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Određen se toga da išta negativno te govori.

1644
01:11:45,000 --> 01:11:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš biti kakva hođiš.

1645
01:11:47,000 --> 01:11:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja te neću suditi.

1646
01:11:49,000 --> 01:11:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ište vidjeti to čudu.

1647
01:11:50,000 --> 01:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je nevjerojatno kolika snaga od jedan puta poteče.

1648
01:11:55,000 --> 01:11:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kolika inteligencije.

1649
01:11:56,000 --> 01:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliki mir.

1650
01:11:57,000 --> 01:11:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko zdrav je.

1651
01:11:58,000 --> 01:11:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Skakao je.

1652
01:11:59,000 --> 01:12:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pravo bih gimnastiku sve do podne.

1653
01:12:01,000 --> 01:12:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] A onda kad još kažeš drugu.

1654
01:12:06,000 --> 01:12:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oprostiti meni.

1655
01:12:08,000 --> 01:12:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam znao do sada biti mudar.

1656
01:12:11,000 --> 01:12:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čist prema tebi.

1657
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:14,000
